ji\" /><br />\n唔開心咪認唔開心，冇乜大不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:41:39.000Z","msg":"成日唔開心 令身邊所有人都唔開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T21:05:21.000Z","msg":"做下啲會令自己開心嘅嘢"},{"pid":"3761ce4af3a8c4e0264207bc6a70c4cf63a6e004","tid":1974274,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa80f52a6aaf3159bb195ba270f88bfc06185cf4","tid":1974274,"uid":127325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T21:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b754eea1cf4ec73db1c9bc6d61f2bc8b922e54cb","tid":1974274,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa80f52a6aaf3159bb195ba270f88bfc06185cf4","tid":1974274,"uid":127325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"&quot;抑鬱閪&quot;，看來... ... &hellip;的痛苦，已令你完全地陷入絕望之中，甚至覺得生無可戀．或許，你認為... ... ...是你人生之中經歷過最大的打擊，因此令你下了這個死亡的決定。不過，在人生眾多重要決定之中，自殺肯定是最矛盾、最痛苦，並且是最重大的。因為，這個決定是一個永不能回轉的決定。我相信，你不是嚮往死亡，只是活得很苦。自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的。<br />\n<br />\n生與死的決定權，總是在自己的手裡，是沒有人能強迫的。你既然已對生存無望，何不拋開一切包袱，停一停下來與我們傾訴一下？<br />\n<br />\n我們的網站是    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=6adb8ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    ，那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（       <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=2688cb67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>      ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴，將你藏在心裡的痛苦，告訴我們吧！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"84ffc6804e8132179dc85c922c4369c6b20a0e53","tid":1974274,"uid":56506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"你冇野做嗰陣我陪你 我都好唔開心 唔好自己一個"},{"pid":"d57f43d0a1bf677a944ac9175197d9b4b0e41585","tid":1974274,"uid":264430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"撐住!<br />\n頂住!"},{"pid":"8306648ef2c935fffc8892d57164481f0f2f21cd","tid":1974274,"uid":230012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"或許人生有許多弄，但再見世界，不在其中。<br />\n留有用之軀，好唔好？"},{"pid":"c10489be01d9db0884a91536e455f21d53d72db4","tid":1974274,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa80f52a6aaf3159bb195ba270f88bfc06185cf4","tid":1974274,"uid":127325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"死之前, 可唔可以幫香港既未來做番啲野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa5609e3f62adae7d83e1f037df6f19dad58e2c","tid":1974274,"uid":314679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"巴打我都好明你感受 不過與其一直諗唔開心野 可以嘗試下做多啲令自己開心啲野 例如打機等等 <br />\n一齊撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be3959a58c609eae0e5e6cc0d0313a4299ce3a7","tid":1974274,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5066d26087ff7e8a0068668815dc5fd3f39c13c","tid":1974274,"uid":127325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e658998320601811b350839cb8ba5cd41b29752e","tid":1974274,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa80f52a6aaf3159bb195